attributes.title: THIS ORANGE MADE MY EYES BLEED 🤮
attributes.review: so i was on youtube and there was hundreds of ads telling me to get this app and i finally did it 🙄🙄😒😒 at first i expected it to be a normal app nothing new but then i opened it AND THIS ORANGE LOOKING CHEETO PUFF SHOWED UP 🤮🤮 AND I SCREAMED AS LOUD AS I COULD THEN THREW MY PHONE ACROSS THE ROOM AND MY EYES STARTED BLEEDING SO MUCH i hope to never see that again it was such a horrible experience i ended up going to the hospital. attributes.title: dude...
attributes.review: literally the most trash app that apple has to offer. i’m switching to android 🤥🤢

When I downloaded this app I was so happy to get more information on ✨President Cheeto✨ but the downloading process took about 3 days. After waiting days I got a FaceTime call on the app from ✨Mr.Cheeto✨ saying he loves Ivanka and always gets boners  around her. As soon as I heard that I disconnected from the app call and left the app immediately afterwards. The next I went on the app hoping nothing would happen and after 10 minutes of being on the app again our presidents nudes were shown on the screen. Then I immediately deleted the app.
